      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><em>Terrifying.</em> If an enemy starts their turn within 5 feet of three or more shades, the enemy must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or be @Compendium[dndbeyond-wel.journal.YTRlYjQyYWY3Mjk0]{frightened} of the shades until the start of their next turn. The DC for this saving throw equals 10 plus the number of shades within 5 feet of the enemy. On a successful save, the enemy is immune to the Terrifying trait of all shades for the next 24 hours.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
        "source": {
